            "value": "<section class=\"details\">\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your turn begins, and you are at half or fewer Hit Points.</p>\n<hr></section>\n<section class=\"content\">\n<p>Your blood boils when you take a beating, and you throw caution to the wind to finish the fight. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to attack rolls, a –2 penalty to AC, and a –1 penalty to saves. These bonuses and penalties last until your Rage ends or until you are above half Hit Points, whichever comes first.</p>\n</section>",
